snippet.title: Celebrities Who Actually DEFENDED Amber Heard on LIVE TV! HERE'S WHY!!
snippet.description:
Celebrities Who Actually DEFENDED Amber Heard on LIVE TV! HERE'S WHY!!

At this point, there is nobody out there who has not at least even heard of the ongoing legal battles between Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard. It has been ongoing for several years now, and after significant development, it is safe to say that the legal conflict is finally reaching its conclusion now. In one of the latest chapters of Johnny Depp’s 50 million dollar defamation suit against Amber. 

The legal team behind Johnny went as far as issuing subpoenas to Amber’s ex-boyfriend, who happens to be the billionaire behind SpaceX, Elon Musk as well as the American Civil Liberties Union Foundation, that Amber had promised half of her 7 Million Dollar divorce settlements will go to. Well, things took a turn when Johnny’s lawyers claimed that they have proof that the money did not go where it should have gone. Watch out for the video to discover more...
